Feature: Apple Secure Enclave Attestation
  As a cloud operator
  I want to verify an attestation object generated by an iOS device using AppAttest
  So that I can confirm the device is genuine before issuing certificates

  Scenario: Apple AppAttest verification flow
    Given an attestation object generated by the iOS device
    When sent to the OpenCertServer for verification
    Then the server should successfully verify the object using https://appattest.apple.com and confirm device genuineness
